snippet.title: Facebook Adds Same-Sex Icons for Gay Marriage
snippet.description:
Facebook Adds Same-Sex Icons for Gay Marriage
Toegevoegd door Buzz60 vorig jaar
Facebook is determined to keep up with Apple when it comes to LGBT inclusion. A few weeks after Apple's popular Emoji added gay and lesbian couple emoticons, Facebook unveiled same-sex picture icons to represent gay marriage. The development came just in time for Facebook co-founder Chris Hughes' marriage to his long-time boyfriend. Rena Karefa-Johnson has more.
